text: Scutellastra obtecta is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Patellidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== ==External links== * Category:Patellidae Category:Gastropods described in 1848 Category:Taxa named by Christian Ferdinand Friedrich Krauss
title: Scutellastra obtecta
